      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total beauty. This car is in showroom condition\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and still has that amazing new-car smell! Not a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a dream and has been treated with so much love. I'm only selling because I'm moving overseas, so I'm looking for a great new owner who will appreciate how pristine this ride is. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
