    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster, enhanced by a professional ceramic coating that makes the finish look liquid under the sun\u2014completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. The alloy wheels are flawless, wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin is a genuine time capsule; the leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and the original factory fragrance remains. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with the crispness of a brand-new car. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a fully documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. Underneath, the chassis is as clean as the body, showing no signs of inclement weather use. This isn't just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment ready for its next steward. No accidents, no modifications, and no compromises.",
      "price": 46500.0,
